{"tid":1565493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求央企加強控制香港 係咪可以解除商家中立協議","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:36:54.000Z","uid":109560,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61f7508c1f60ab3a617a605a2f2d4ae0bdc1cbb2","tid":1565493,"uid":109560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"相信大家攻擊黨鐵，立會，中聯辦都係因為佢地代表政府<br />\n而央企打算加強對香港企業既控制<br />\n代表呢一部分既企業都係政府既代表<br />\n<br />\n到而家為止都無私人企業既財產成為目標<br />\n因為商家唔屬於政府既一部分<br />\n而央企幫政府控制香港而加強對企業控制<br />\n代表佢地已經係<span style=\"color: red;\">政府代表</span><br />\n被排除在禁止攻擊項目入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且目標多而廣<br />\n好難好似中聯辦咁守住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：央企將會被排除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：繼續當佢地商家，禁止攻擊"},{"pid":"8d023198f3ca53c552eaa86336f9127c170acb02","tid":1565493,"uid":109560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"在香港有上市兼且有業務來往的央企，如中石化、中移動、中遠洋、招商局、中國中鐵、保利集團、中石油、中國建築等等"},{"pid":"cc4f1980fa9d341ac1e449ff79000645261cc355","tid":1565493,"uid":109560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"華潤集團：華潤堂，vingo，Pacific coffee"},{"pid":"7ee7411fc43c46657be785844ba85a3efef2727b","tid":1565493,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都唔知有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔對得住烈士同被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /